        </div>
        <h2>Built in the open.</h2>
        <p>Chops is completely free and open source under the MIT license. Read the code, submit a PR, or fork it and make it your own. We think the best tools are the ones you can trust.</p>
        <a href="https://github.com/Shpigford/chops" class="oss-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
          Star on GitHub
          <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="7" y1="17" x2="17" y2="7"/><polyline points="7 7 17 7 17 17"/></svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .oss {
    padding: 20px 32px 100px;
    background: var(--bg);
  }

  .oss-inner {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .oss-card {
    position: relative;
    background: var(--text);
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 64px;
    overflow: hidden;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .oss-glow {
    position: absolute;
    top: -50%;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    width: 400px;
    height: 400px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,109,97,0.2) 0%, transparent 60%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .oss-content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .oss-icon {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 64px;
    height: 64px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    border-radius: 16px;
    color: white;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .oss-card h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: white;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .oss-card p {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
    max-width: 460px;
    margin: 0 auto 28px;
  }

  .oss-link {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    padding: 12px 28px;
    background: white;
    color: var(--text);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    font-weight: 650;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
  }

  .oss-link:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .oss-card {
      padding: 40px 24px;
    }

    .oss-card h2 {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }

    .oss {
      padding: 20px 20px 64px;
    }
  }
</style>
